{"tid":1337144,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問，上氣係咪即係熱氣既意思呀？","createTime":"2019-07-21T08:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T08:09:24.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6260d6acb399e45b7db3666ad37e7d398f7aa9bd","tid":1337144,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc53b3e6d2bbe8b5efbe9c9bc1b9ed75b5105dbc","tid":1337144,"uid":188282,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"上氣&rdquo;即肺氣上逆之意。此症臨床上有實證、虛證的區別。實證主要症狀為喘咳胸滿、呼吸迫促、不能平臥、痰多粘膩、脈浮滑，是由於肺實氣閉所致。虛證主要症狀為咳喘面浮、脈浮大無力，這是&ldquo;腎不納氣&rdquo;所致"}]}